headline: Assurant Partners with Arcadium Technologies to Optimize Truck Protection Product Sales by Commercial Truck Dealers
summary: ATLANTA, August 26, 2025--Assurant, Inc. (NYSE: AIZ), a premier global protection company that safeguards and services connected devices, homes and automobiles in partnership with the world’s leading brands, today announced a partnership with Arcadium Technologies, LLC, a leading provider of Customer Relationship Management (CRM), vehicle inventory, and vehicle sales management tools to heavy-duty truck, trailer, and equipment dealers.
